to build project use
& "C:\Program Files\Microsoft Visual Studio\2022\Community\MSBuild\Current\Bin\MSBuild.exe" "src\RengaDynMain.csproj" /p:Configuration=Debug /p:Platform=x64 /verbosity:minimal
or
& "C:\Program Files\Microsoft Visual Studio\18\Insiders\MSBuild\Current\Bin\MSBuild.exe" "src\RengaDynMain.csproj" /p:Configuration=Debug /p:Platform=x64 /verbosity:minimal   

Allways Use context7 if you working with renga api
<https://context7.com/websites/help_rengabim_api>

Do not output debug info to the console log. Output it to the second output (DebugInfo) of the node.

Allways add new wrapers to the project before build
